const ReportsView: React.FC<{ logs: HabitLog, getDayChecks: (d: string) => boolean[], onSelectDate: (d: string) => void, habitNames: string[] }> = ({ logs, getDayChecks, onSelectDate, habitNames }) => {
    const [viewMode, setViewMode] = useState<'analytics' | 'history'>('analytics');

    // Stats for Analytics
    const { pieData, barData, totalDays, monthlyData } = useMemo(() => {
        const scoreDist = [0, 0, 0, 0]; // 0: Inactive, 1: Average, 2: Good, 3: Perfect
        const habitCounts = new Array(10).fill(0);
        let total = 0;
        const monthMap: Record<string, { total: number; count: number }> = {};

        Object.entries(logs).forEach(([dateStr, val]) => {
            const checks = val as boolean[]; // Explicit cast to handle unknown type inference
            if (!checks || checks.length === 0) return;
            total++;
            const score = checks.filter(Boolean).length;

            // Pie Distribution
            if (score === 10) scoreDist[3]++;
            else if (score >= 6) scoreDist[2]++;
            else if (score >= 1) scoreDist[1]++;
            else scoreDist[0]++;

            // Habit Bar Data
            checks.forEach((c, i) => {
                if (c) habitCounts[i]++;
            });

            // Monthly Trend
            const monthKey = format(parseISO(dateStr), 'MMM yyyy');
            if (!monthMap[monthKey]) monthMap[monthKey] = { total: 0, count: 0 };
            monthMap[monthKey].total += score;
            monthMap[monthKey].count += 1;
        });

        const pie = [
            { label: 'Perfect (10)', value: scoreDist[3], color: '#10b981' }, // Emerald
            { label: 'Good (6-9)', value: scoreDist[2], color: '#3b82f6' }, // Blue
            { label: 'Average (1-5)', value: scoreDist[1], color: '#f59e0b' }, // Amber
            { label: 'Inactive (0)', value: scoreDist[0], color: '#ef4444' }, // Red
        ].filter(d => d.value > 0);

        const bar = habitNames.map((name, i) => ({
            label: name,
            value: habitCounts[i],
            percentage: total > 0 ? Math.round((habitCounts[i] / total) * 100) : 0,
            color: VIBRANT_COLORS[i % VIBRANT_COLORS.length]
        })).sort((a, b) => b.value - a.value);

        const monthly = Object.entries(monthMap).map(([label, data]) => ({
            label,
            value: Math.round((data.total / data.count) * 10) / 10, // Average score
            color: '#6366f1'
        })).slice(-12); // Last 12 months

        return { pieData: pie, barData: bar, totalDays: total, monthlyData: monthly };
    }, [logs, habitNames]);

    const sortedDates = Object.keys(logs || {}).sort().reverse();

    return (
        <div className="space-y-6 animate-fade-in pb-10" key={habitNames.join(',')}>
            <div className="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Reports & Analytics</h2>
                <div className="flex bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-1 rounded-lg">
                    <button
                        onClick={() => setViewMode('analytics')}
                        className={`px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold rounded-md transition-all ${
                            viewMode === 'analytics' 
                            ? 'bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 shadow-sm' 
                            : 'text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-200'
                        }`}
                    >
                        Charts
                    </button>
                    <button
                        onClick={() => setViewMode('history')}
                        className={`px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold rounded-md transition-all ${
                            viewMode === 'history' 
                            ? 'bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 shadow-sm' 
                            : 'text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-200'
                        }`}
                    >
                        History
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            {viewMode === 'analytics' && (
                <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    {/* Pie Chart Card */}
                    <div className="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm p-6">
                        <h3 className="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <div className="p-1.5 bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 rounded-md text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"><PieChartIcon className="w-4 h-4"/></div>
                            Consistency Breakdown
                        </h3>
                        <DonutChart data={pieData} total={totalDays} />
                    </div>

                    {/* Bar Chart Card */}
                    <div className="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm p-6">
                         <h3 className="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <div className="p-1.5 bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 rounded-md text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400"><ListIcon className="w-4 h-4"/></div>
                            Habit Performance
                        </h3>
                        <HorizontalBarChart data={barData} />
                    </div>

                    {/* Trend Graph Card */}
                    <div className="md:col-span-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm p-6">
                         <h3 className="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <div className="p-1.5 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-md text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400"><ChartBarIcon className="w-4 h-4"/></div>
                            Monthly Average Score
                        </h3>
                        {monthlyData.length > 0 ? (
                            <VerticalBarGraph data={monthlyData} />
                        ) : (
                            <div className="h-32 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 text-sm">Insufficient data for trends</div>
                        )}
                    </div>
                </div>
            )}

            {viewMode === 'history' && (
                <div className="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                    <div className="divide-y divide-slate-100 dark:divide-slate-700">
                    {sortedDates.length === 0 && (
                        <div className="p-12 text-center text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
                            No data recorded yet.
                        </div>
                    )}
                    {sortedDates.map(date => {
                        const count = getDayChecks(date).filter(Boolean).length;
                        return (
                            <div key={date} onClick={() => onSelectDate(date)} className="p-4 sm:p-5 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700/50 cursor-pointer transition-colors flex items-center justify-between group">
                                <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
                                    <div className={`w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg text-white shadow-sm ${getScoreColor(count)}`}>
                                        {count}
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p className="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">{format(parseISO(date), 'MMMM do, yyyy')}</p>
                                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">{format(parseISO(date), 'EEEE')}</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <ChevronDownIcon className="w-5 h-5 text-slate-300 group-hover:text-indigo-500 -rotate-90 transition-colors" />
                            </div>
                        );
                    })}
                    </div>
                </div>
            )}
        </div>
    );
};

